  <thing id="fSGStrgFnd" name="Strong Foundation" description="You can grit your teeth and concentrate on the courage you possess to apply it against other mind-affecting abilities. \n\n{b}Prerequisite{/b}: Aura of courage class feature\n\n{b}Benefit{/b}: When you would normally be charmed or dominated, as a swift action at the beginning of each round you may choose to instead be staggered for one round. Anything that removes this staggered condition also restores the charm or dominated effect." compset="Feat" uniqueness="useronce">
